Date: 2001-02-15

Title: Quantum discontinuity between zero and infinitesimal graviton mass with

a Lambda termAuthors: F. A. Dilkes, M. J. Duff, James T. Liu and H. Sati

Comments: 8 pages, revtex 3.1, title changed (version to appear in Phys. Rev.

Lett.)Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 87 (2001) 041301

We show that the recently demonstrated absence of the usual discontinuity formassive spin 2 with a Lambda term is an artifact of the tree approximation, andthat the discontinuity reappears at one loop.